{"tid":1672394,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"［短故］《坐緊巴士，坐我前面嘅男仔突然爆喊》","createTime":"2019-10-24T05:41:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T16:12:21.000Z","uid":216390,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"db32d733890ab6f8458db17d3db1ab7b303325d9","tid":1672394,"uid":216390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家好，今次係本人第二次係連登出文，希望各位可以花時間睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次係一篇短故，主要係講述女主角坐車嘅時候發現前面嗰男仔突然喊。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n以下亦都係我曾經係紙言寫過嘅故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有興趣可以睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://post.shikoto.com/authors/37153\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpost.shikoto.com%2Fauthors%2F37153&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUofo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=ea63d374\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://post.shikoto.com/authors/37153</a>"},{"pid":"0a5f05f4bbd296d22a41f07e9f9bd31cf421880f","tid":1672394,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:41:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>SUCK 1026長龍爆買日<br />\n18區爆買日目標黃店（二）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EOOhfyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEOOhfyX.png&h=d91ed7f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/19AO6FF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F19AO6FF.png&h=57f7abed&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5e3d8034c3a75c4f256cd22e9393bc70853bb4ee","tid":1672394,"uid":216390,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:42:04.000Z","msg":"佢唔係我男朋友，又或者咁講，我連佢個樣都記唔清楚，我哋只係巴士上嘅其中一位乘客，但唔知點解，我覺得我會記住佢一世。<br />\n<br />\n我係一個好鐘意坐巴士上層窗口位嘅人，得閒就望下風景同發夢，不過好似有心事嘅人會對住風景諗起自己鐘意或者失去嘅對象。對於我呢啲無拍過拖嘅人，就無辦法想像得到佢哋嘅心情。<br />\n<br />\n係某日嘅夜晚11點幾，我因為喺學校趕final year project遲咗走，坐咗架平時無坐機會坐到嘅班次，以為咁夜會無乜人，點知去到上層，居然仲有一兩個人坐，但之後都無理太多，隨便揀個位，再戴上耳筒，隨即進入屬於自己嘅音樂世界。<br />\n<br />\n我望住窗外風景，無意係反射之中見到坐我前面嘅男仔，佢一直望住手機螢幕，時不時又留意去到邊個站，雖然我個角度睇唔清楚，但隱約見到係男女kiss嘅一張合照，於是我推測佢應該係好心急咁等女朋友，乜鐘意一個人真係見少一秒都唔得？有時候，我都好想感受下呢種所謂嘅煎熬。"},{"pid":"da97de519d0e428ef1afa6b0c85b0c52af6d9458","tid":1672394,"uid":216390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a5f05f4bbd296d22a41f07e9f9bd31cf421880f","tid":1672394,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:41:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>SUCK 1026長龍爆買日<br />\n18區爆買日目標黃店（二）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EOOhfyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEOOhfyX.png&h=d91ed7f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/19AO6FF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F19AO6FF.png&h=57f7abed&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:43:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e57be1266ce17cc06a6c555ef122b4ef02f560","tid":1672394,"uid":216390,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:44:40.000Z","msg":"無幾耐，巴士準備埋站到糖水鋪附近嗰時，佢突然對住窗口喊，唔係流曬眼淚鼻涕嗰種，而係撕心裂肺嘅飲泣，佢每發出嘅微弱喊聲，我都感受到佢嘅心酸，我諗佢之所以望住幅相，應該係好掛住對方。<br />\n<br />\n唔知邊度嚟嘅勇氣，我居然從車窗嘅罅隙向佢遞咗張紙巾：「佢同你分手係佢唔識珍惜你姐，下個一定更好㗎。」無錯，身為A0嘅我竟然安慰人失戀同提供戀愛意見。聽到我呢番說話，佢好似有少少嚇親，但都有接過我張紙巾，就係咁，我哋展開咗對話。<br />\n<br />\n「Errr...係咪我嘈到你，唔好意思，我都無諗過自己會咁。」佢仍然帶有少少哭腔，我即時話唔緊要，然後佢又繼續講：「我諗你應該係以為我啱啱被人飛？」「係啊，因為我見你喊得好慘......」我小心翼翼咁回應，避免再次觸碰到佢嘅淚線。<br />\n<br />\n「其實我唔係被人飛，係我同佢講分手，而且我哋已經分咗手一個月。」從車窗所反射嘅倒影，佢情緒似乎平靜咗好多。"},{"pid":"275bfd2f800adeabfcf0e3cb4267531400a8223b","tid":1672394,"uid":216390,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:12:23.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />夜少少再出"},{"pid":"880ff70484aed2caad6b07398de45b575fc469fd","tid":1672394,"uid":48942,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:48:18.000Z","msg":"停咗喺依個位唔係好吸引到人"},{"pid":"2c19ae450f3999131fe218f5de4f096cf753cb70","tid":1672394,"uid":320293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:03:37.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"d8f65dcd07995789f82c884401551bfe063cdd97","tid":1672394,"uid":216390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"880ff70484aed2caad6b07398de45b575fc469fd","tid":1672394,"uid":48942,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:48:18.000Z","msg":"停咗喺依個位唔係好吸引到人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:01:39.000Z","msg":"收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會改善下 <br />\n多謝你意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be0583b8ef155a3ec7bcf433f762f86f591d5dd6","tid":1672394,"uid":216390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:04:30.000Z","msg":"吓？乜......佢先係同人講分手嗰個？仲已經過咗成個月？OMG......好尷尬，頭先我仲係度扮愛情專家咁安慰人，不過，咦？個個都話講分手係衰人，但佢睇落仲好鐘意人，點解要講分手？<br />\n<br />\n可能佢意識到我有好多疑問，又或者單純想揾人聽下佢講嘢，佢開始解釋來龍去脈。<br />\n<br />\n「好奇怪呢？點解咁鐘意佢仲要講分手，點解已經過咗一個月，仲要為佢係架車上面喊。<br />\n<br />\n講分手，唔係因為唔鐘意，而係因為太鐘意。<br />\n<br />\n我同佢只係短短一齊咗一年，但我一直當佢係結婚對象，只係無諗到，佢會咁快對我淡咗，我有試過去配合佢，同佢講下我哋未來計劃，希望佢可以揾翻種感覺。"},{"pid":"bba3577f4f7740f1d9ba10bc9619bbec44cf3701","tid":1672394,"uid":216390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:05:17.000Z","msg":"可惜無用啊，我知佢都有挽回過，嘗試變翻以前嘅感覺，但佢越係努力，我就越感覺到佢早已對我無感覺。<br />\n<br />\n如果一段感情無咗愛，愛無咗個心，咁段關係仲可以點維持？<br />\n<br />\n表面上嘅我哋好似拖住手好幸福，有講唔完嘅話題，事實上，佢只係不斷揾話題去掩飾彼此嘅陌生感，我好清楚知道，佢已經唔愛我。<br />\n<br />\n既然係咁，再拖落去都係浪費大家時間，佢又辛苦，我又辛苦，咁又何必？兩個人一齊係為咗開心，而唔係折磨㗎。<br />\n<br />\n所以，我決定咗要同佢講分手。<br />\n<br />\n當佢聽到我話要分手之後就即時爆喊，我都忍唔住一齊喊，最後奇奇怪怪咁兩個人係條街到一齊喊。<br />\n<br />\n大概係佢無諗過我會知道佢真正諗法，傻妹，我係你男朋友啊，你嘅諗法我又點會唔知？ <br />\n<br />\n記得佢當時不斷話大家可以再努力多陣，或者可以行到落去，我反問佢愛唔愛我，可惜佢望住我唔出聲，而到最後，我都係堅持要分手。<br />\n<br />\n分手嗰晚，我喊咗好耐，其實如果佢當時話愛我，我應該會回心轉意唔分手，但佢連一句愛我都講唔出，我真係諗唔到之後可以點行落去。"},{"pid":"efc3015b72bb9c5aa8fe88cd05f9f184c31ed94a","tid":1672394,"uid":216390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T12:36:06.000Z","msg":"原本今日係我同佢嘅拍拖三週年，嗰一間糖水鋪，係佢最鐘意去嘅餐廳，但因為覺得貴而唔肯去，於是我哋拍拖紀念日都會係嗰度慶祝，每次我接佢放工就會一齊坐車，然後再係呢個站落車。<br />\n<br />\n分手無耐，我都係好掛住佢，我忍唔住每星期都坐呢架巴士去回憶呢兩年嘅每分每秒，同時亦應承咗自己，每坐一次，就會delete 一張同佢係糖水鋪影嘅合照，本身當delete 曬同佢嘅合照就唔會再坐呢架車，永遠放低佢。頭先，我已經delete 咗同佢嘅最後一張相。<br />\n<br />\n但我到底要點做，先可以delete 到對佢嘅感情？」話畢，佢好似又忍唔住流眼淚。"},{"pid":"eeeb497e897cb18ced3ffc0a68b2320fc2413f3e","tid":1672394,"uid":216390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:35:45.000Z","msg":"聽日繼續"},{"pid":"9f1c5cefb6e5aea0597d068e78e7bc183f062445","tid":1672394,"uid":48942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:50:34.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"53bd77bfc7e2e7fce74a6ec08dbe493ddce8ca36","tid":1672394,"uid":216390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f1c5cefb6e5aea0597d068e78e7bc183f062445","tid":1672394,"uid":48942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:50:34.000Z","msg":"加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:07:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝"},{"pid":"cc17b12d40496f794de9fc94434ee51e31f5e684","tid":1672394,"uid":14566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:27:29.000Z","msg":"甜呢"},{"pid":"322b3a1429a4a516e6c61b21e11c6294de782f17","tid":1672394,"uid":216390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc17b12d40496f794de9fc94434ee51e31f5e684","tid":1672394,"uid":14566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:27:29.000Z","msg":"甜呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T09:29:20.000Z","msg":"睇落去就知有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d5b507144d0a72a0c8d84661daa83ce5219bddd","tid":1672394,"uid":216390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:42:25.000Z","msg":"我有少少驚訝，我以為講分手嘅人必定係狠心，而且唔會留戀同絕情，睇落係愛情上，我的確係入世未深。<br />\n<br />\n我消化咗一陣佢所講嘅說話，然後回應：「或者，佢而加可能會想一齊翻？有時候分開下先知對方嘅重要㗎，揾下佢啦，試下無妨嘛。」<br />\n<br />\n「無可能啦，要留一早留到，加上我見佢而加IG都好享受一個人生活，佢之後都有Whatsapp翻千字文比我，我哋之間無嘢好講㗎啦。」佢感慨。<br />\n<br />\n「佢寫咗咩比你？啊，我純粹好奇，如果咁問會令你唔開心就算，當我無問過。」我慌張咁解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「唔會啦，我都打算要放低佢，話俾你聽都好，多一個人去為我同佢記住呢份感情。<br />\n<br />\n佢寫嘅一字一句，我仲記得好清楚。<br />\n<br />\n<em>呢兩年好多謝你照顧，你一直都對我好好，當我唔開心嘅時候，你會攬實我，聽我講心事；我被腦細話無用，你又會同我一齊講佢壞話；係我最開心嘅時候，身邊有你陪我去感受，呢兩年，我真心過得好知足。<br />\n<br />\n但相處耐咗，就開始發覺大家係愛情上嘅價值觀好唔同，有時候我都會想要翻啲私人空間你唔係無比到，但你仲好想成日見。見下見下，我都攰啦，我想休息下，想一個人單獨靜下。<br />\n<br />\n對唔住，我無耐性同你一齊行埋落去，你一定要揾過比我好嘅人陪自己。再見。</em><br />\n<br />\n嗰次之後，我哋再無聯絡。如果真係好掛住佢，我就會偷偷地上IG睇佢而加過成點，佢生活得開心，我就心滿意足。」"},{"pid":"9cbd155226896c89b3869b313e4e3f12ea693726","tid":1672394,"uid":216390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:04:37.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"eee343f18f665295a657c5f0b4865ec8e43dcea1","tid":1672394,"uid":192968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db32d733890ab6f8458db17d3db1ab7b303325d9","tid":1672394,"uid":216390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家好，今次係本人第二次係連登出文，希望各位可以花時間睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次係一篇短故，主要係講述女主角坐車嘅時候發現前面嗰男仔突然喊。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n以下亦都係我曾經係紙言寫過嘅故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有興趣可以睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://post.shikoto.com/authors/37153\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpost.shikoto.com%2Fauthors%2F37153&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUofo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=ea63d374\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://post.shikoto.com/authors/37153</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:06:34.000Z","msg":"相信而家上連登既朋友....無咩心情睇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca6c6b2b3a74ec6e3034a0b2e232ee3eda6b347","tid":1672394,"uid":216390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eee343f18f665295a657c5f0b4865ec8e43dcea1","tid":1672394,"uid":192968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db32d733890ab6f8458db17d3db1ab7b303325d9","tid":1672394,"uid":216390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家好，今次係本人第二次係連登出文，希望各位可以花時間睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次係一篇短故，主要係講述女主角坐車嘅時候發現前面嗰男仔突然喊。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n以下亦都係我曾經係紙言寫過嘅故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有興趣可以睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://post.shikoto.com/authors/37153\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpost.shikoto.com%2Fauthors%2F37153&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUofo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=ea63d374\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://post.shikoto.com/authors/37153</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:06:34.000Z","msg":"相信而家上連登既朋友....無咩心情睇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T16:12:21.000Z","msg":"你都啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都考慮咗好耐應唔應該開Po  <br />\n不過我又心急想試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}